revision.text:
The '''War of 1812 bibliography''' is a selective, [[annotated bibliography]] using [[APA style]] [[citation]]s of the many books related to the [[War of 1812]]. There are thousands of books and articles written about this topic. Only the most useful are presented.

==Overviews==
* {{cite book|last=Adams|first=Henry|title=History of the United States of America During the Administrations of James Madison|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IZqMDXn6nwoC&pg=PP1|year=1986|orig-year=1891|publisher=Library of America|isbn=978-0-940450-35-6}}
