{{Portal|Ancient Near East}} The '''''Journal of Cuneiform Studies''''' was founded in 1947 by the [[Baghdad]] School of the [[American Schools of Oriental Research]]. The journal presents articles about ancient [[Mesopotamian]] language and history in [[English language|English]], [[French language|French]] and [[German language|German]].
